<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About UniBite</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Learn about UniBite - making campus dining quick, easy, and convenient for the MIU community">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Styles/styles.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/Styles/about.css">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
<%- include('partials/Header', { active: 'about' }) %>

<main class="about-page">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h1>About UniBite</h1>
      <p>Making campus dining quick, easy, and convenient for the MIU community</p>
    </div>

    
    <section class="mission-section">
      <div class="mission-grid">
        <div class="mission-content">
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            UniBite was created by MIU students who were tired of waiting in long lines between classes just to grab a
            quick bite. We believe that campus dining should be efficient, allowing students and faculty to focus on
            what matters most - education and campus life.
          </p>
          <ul class="check-list">
            <li>Save time by skipping the lines at campus eateries</li>
            <li>Provide a platform exclusively for the MIU community</li>
            <li>Support local campus businesses and food vendors</li>
            <li>Make campus dining more efficient and enjoyable</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-image">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/600x400/f0f0f0/666?text=MIU+Campus" alt="MIU Campus">
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    
    <section class="stats-section">
      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">2,500+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Active Users</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">6</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Campus Restaurants</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">15,000+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Orders Completed</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <div class="stat-number">30 min</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Average Time Saved</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    
    <section class="values-section">
      <h2>Our Values</h2>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Community First</h3>
          <p>We build for the MIU community, focusing on their unique needs and challenges.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <circle cx="12" cy="8" r="7"></circle>
              <polyline points="8.21 13.89 7 23 12 20 17 23 15.79 13.88"></polyline>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Quality Service</h3>
          <p>We're committed to providing reliable, high-quality service to every user.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="value-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"></path>
              <path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Continuous Improvement</h3>
          <p>We constantly seek feedback and improve our platform to better serve the community.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    
    <section class="contact-section">
      <h2>Want to get in touch?</h2>
      <p>We're always looking for feedback and ways to improve UniBite for the MIU community.</p>
      <div class="contact-buttons">
        <a href="mailto:contact@unibite.com" class="btn btn-white">Email Us</a>
        <a href="help" class="btn btn-outline-white">Visit Help Center</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</main>


<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer-content">
      <div class="footer-copyright">
        <p>&copy; <span id="current-year">2025</span> UniBite. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="about-us">About</a>
        <a href="help">Help</a>
        <a href="privacy">Privacy</a>
        <a href="terms">Terms</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>

<script src="JavaScript/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
